OL,5, The widow of a nurse who died from     
OL,6, Covid is suing the NHS as she believes 
OL,7, her husband was not "looked after".    
OL,9,FA coroner concluded 65-year-old Gareth 
OL,10,FRoberts died of "industrial disease",  
OL,11,Fhaving probably contracted Covid-19 at 
OL,12,Fwork.                                  
OL,14,FIt is thought to be the first time a   
OL,15,Fcoroner has made such a finding for a  
OL,16,Fdeath from the virus.                  
OL,18,FCardiff and Vale University Health     
OL,19,FBoard said Mr Roberts was a "very      
OL,20,Fvalued" colleague.                     
